sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Go/pgx
    participant P as Primary
    participant S as Sync Replica
    participant D as DCS

    A->>P: BEGIN/UPDATE/COMMIT
    P->>P: 修改 Buffer，生成 WAL
    P->>P: WAL flush 到本地持久介质
    P->>S: WAL streaming
    S->>S: write/flush（取决于 synchronous_commit）
    S-->>P: 同步确认
    P-->>A: COMMIT 成功
    P->>D: Patroni 周期性续约 Leader Lock/发布状态
